name: Clint Marseille organic hemp jersey toy man
description:
Clint is a lovely organic hemp jersey toy, printed with eco friendly ink in Wales and hand assembled in our studio!
Born in France Clint grew up in East London, he loves eating croissants with mushy peas, yum!

He can be washed with cool water and dried flat! Approx 35cm tall he is made to European standards and carries the CE mark.

name: Tarquin jersey toy
description:
Tarquin is a lovely Grey marl jersey toy is made using fabric manufactured in the U.K, printed with eco friendly ink in Wales and hand assembled in our studio!

He can be washed with cool water and dried flat! Approx 35cm tall he is made to European standards and carries the CE mark.

Here's some more info about him:
Despite appearances, Tarquin (that’s Tarquers to his friends), often eats more than 3 packets of crisps a day. Tarquin likes to think of himself as a trend setter. The trend he is currently trying to set is the brown sock and bow tie combo, but he would be quick to remind you, that this outfit choice is for tuesdays only.

name: Wilby Toy
description:
A calm and collected character, Wilby enjoys the methodical joys of life. He likes to take a step back and have a think about the situation, whether this be his badge collection or the time when he spent over 3 and a half hours trying to count all the straight lines he could see out of the window. However, all this thinking does not a smart Wilby make. Once he was swindled by con artist that sold him forged autographs from D list celebrities. He added them to his collection regardless.  

Wilby is a lovely Grey marl jersey toy is made using fabric manufactured in the U.K, printed with eco friendly ink in Wales and hand assembled in our studio!

Wilby collects badges and autographs so he may ask for yours!

He can be washed with cool water and dried flat! Approx 35cm tall he is made to European standards and carries the CE mark.

name: Barry Bags toy
description:
Where do we start with Barry Bags. His face is the only thing bigger than his reputation. Partial to sherbet fountains he is a charmer with a huge social circle. He may come across as a fickle socialite, but don’t be fooled. He knows the names (including middle names) of everyone he calls a mate. Ask any of them and you will find out he is a true reliable friend that will always be there for you. Having said this, do not turn your back when he is armed with a Liquorice whip.  

And he is a lovely Grey marl jersey toy is made using fabric manufactured in the U.K, printed with eco friendly ink in Wales and hand assembled in our studio!

He can be washed with cool water and dried flat! Approx 35cm tall he is made to European standards and carries the CE mark.

name: Interactive World weather map
description:
An A2 size map of the world complete with 8 weather symbols! Now you can predict the weather across this globe we call planet Earth! 

The felt is made in the U.S then hand-printed with eco-friendly ink in Wales before being sewn at our studio In London.

Conforming to CE standards the map is not suitable for the under 3's due to small parts.

He is approximately 50cm tall and nearly as wide. He would be very happy on your sofa or being cuddled on a beach in Tenerife. He comes in 2 colours: Blue marl and caramel!

His middle name is Percy.
